methods.getObject:
Get a single object from this region.

*Overload 1*  
  :param elementIndex: (long) - Element (object) index in the table's address space
  :return: (DeferredColumnRegionObject.T) The object value at the specified element (object) index
  
*Overload 2*  
  :param context: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.ChunkSource.FillContext) - A ColumnRegionFillContext to enable resource caching where suitable, with current
                       region index pointing to this region
  :param elementIndex: (long) - Element (object) index in the table's address space
  :return: (DeferredColumnRegionObject.T) The object value at the specified element (object) index
